{"tid":975840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[爆料］杜汶澤專惹事生非，忘恩負義，是有燥狂症的人！ 蕭若元：我絕不會同佢做朋友！","createTime":"2019-01-10T03:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T16:11:16.000Z","uid":49388,"like":74,"dislike":203,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"b2793540727517067fa4b872c074906e93283615","tid":975840,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:36:28.000Z","msg":"係咪反共就等於好人？ 蕭生：不是，劉華與杜汶澤就是例子<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NJJmuq-s6V4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNJJmuq-s6V4&d=XYjAR2kfDNRlBgPoxB6BaMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=0bf0d734\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NJJmuq-s6V4</a><br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤是不停惹事生非的人，大多數激進派都係咁<br />\n<br />\n劉華曾資助杜汶澤拍戲，結果唔收得唔肯再資助拍第二部，之後反被杜汶澤批評生仔無屎忽，激到劉華紥紥跳<br />\n<br />\n吳君如亦有幫過杜汶澤，但杜汶澤一樣在背後講人壞話<br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤又週街差人錢<br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤又結過三次婚個D唔講<br />\n<br />\n所以反共不等於好人，警察唔一定全部係黑警<br />\n<br />\n若果所以野非黑即白，幫過政府做事表演等等就係壞人<br />\n<br />\n泛民又被你地打成壞人，唔支持你就係港豬，最後只會孤立自己沒有同路人。<br />\n<br />\n蕭生絕不會同杜汶澤呢D人做朋友！"},{"pid":"f62338d8907c5d80540ee6987a19ba81da16da9b","tid":975840,"uid":37358,"like":242,"dislike":2,"score":240,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:38:30.000Z","msg":"顧掂自己個仔先"},{"pid":"525085f9a0dc89a81bfd3e8c514c4ee7d6164a66","tid":975840,"uid":198583,"like":21,"dislike":80,"score":-59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:38:42.000Z","msg":"杜文澤好似鬼鬼地..."},{"pid":"6845926694249d6c135e716dd161629d0eff70ed","tid":975840,"uid":23635,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:38:46.000Z","msg":"燒山好野"},{"pid":"2ab9d545ef7f5bdfefd9baf4bd2105db29784de7","tid":975840,"uid":53687,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:38:49.000Z","msg":"睇完堆字，反顯得燒山先係非黑即白<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89a0e1764c6f45bc1c48000a85aa39890c76f76","tid":975840,"uid":153245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:41:21.000Z","msg":"唉 試問有誰無過呢"},{"pid":"8d65bfa7b4bf